@NODE "Introduction" "Allocator.guide/Introduction"
@NEXT "Instalation"

                           ··· INTRODUCTION ···

      Sorry for my english!  It's very poor, but I trying... :))


		This is a short help for new version Allocator utility.  Allocator is
very  easy i simply to use util to allocating and deallocating any types of
memory.   I  was  created  it  for testing many programs.  Sometimes I must
looking like work my program if memory is low and very low!

      Allocator  was written in 100% in AmigaE.  AmigaE the best compiler for Amiga
systems utils.

      It's all!  I think that small util will good work for your system and
help you in your memory problems!


@ENDNODE

@NODE "Instalation" "Allocator.guide/Instalation"
@PREV "Introduction"
@NEXT "Requirements"

                            ··· INSTALATION ···

      Instalation  Allocator is very easy.  You must click on 'Instal' icon
only.   It'a  all.   If you have installing Allocator without Installer you
must  create  direcotory and copy all files to this directory.  So...  it's
all.

      For   polish  users  in  directory  'Polish'  is  polish  version  of
Allocator.  Polish guide avaible now!!!

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Requirements" "Allocator.guide/Requirements"
@PREV "Instalation"
@NEXT "Usage"

                        ··· SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS ···

      What you need to good and no problem work with Allocator?  It's easy.
You must have:

 · Amiga
 · Kick 2.0+
 · Many RAM to allocate
 · reqtools.library /included 38.3414/
 · XenPL.font /included/

@ENDNODE

@NODE "Usage" "Allocator.guide/Usage"
@PREV "Requirements"
@NEXT "Author"

                               ··· USAGE ···

      Using  this  small  util  is  very easy.  You may choose type memory.
After  you  enter  memeory  by allocate and press Enter!  It's all.  If you
want  deallocate /:>/ used memory, you must click on 'Free' button and all!
It's very easy and full intuition!  :>

      Now ascii screen from Allocator:

     .______________________________________________________________.
     | Free Chip: 1893784  Fast Free: 12451831 |         _________  |
