     `ŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻŻ'
		In   this  version  I  added  help  'online'.   You  must  have  file
'Allocator.guide' in the same directory with Allocator.

      This  program you may execute from CLI and WorkBench.  From CLI added
two options:

- SHADOW - make nice /IMHO/ border
- INFO - write some infos about me in CLI window

		From WorkBench you may add this to ToolType, but I'm not sure... This
may work bad. Sorry.

